<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠٢٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5820">‌ابْنُ الْعَلَاءِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">‌وَكِيعٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">‌سُفْيَانَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2690">‌سُهَيْلٍ </a>نَحْوَهُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«فِي الصَّلَاةِ فَلْيَكْظِمْ مَا اسْتَطَاعَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>